            "title": "東亞去年純利按年增11.9% 擬派第2次中期息每股0.38元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東亞銀行(00023)公布，2024年度歸屬集團股東溢利46.08億元，按年增加11.9%；擬派第2次中期息每股增至0.38元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14719880-%e6%9d%b1%e4%ba%9e%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e11-9-%e6%93%ac%e6%b4%be%e7%ac%ac2%e6%ac%a1%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a10-38%e5%85%83",
